            "STEP 1: Click 'Load Spawn Data'\n"
            "STEP 2: Use Quick Actions to modify spawns\n"
            "STEP 3: Click 'Apply to Game' (restart game to see changes)\n\n"
            "QUICK ACTIONS:\n"
